{"tid":1308151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吉野家牛肉飯食譜","createTime":"2019-07-11T22:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:31:17.000Z","uid":22054,"like":152,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e713baeea30aca0e2383e305b675ce11000a12f9","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:36:31.000Z","msg":"味琳<br />\n豉油<br />\n鰹魚汁/湯<br />\n酒<br />\n<br />\n全部1:1 <br />\n<br />\n洋蔥切條，蒜蓉+薑蓉，牛肉<br />\n<br />\n先炒左洋蔥，落DD糖，炒到熟熟地，加埋D蓉，有香味就倒曬D野落去（中意就加D糖，唔中意就算），較味（唔夠鹹就自己落D鼓油）<br />\n<br />\n滾熟食得，過程唔洗半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國呢面經常煮"},{"pid":"3259ddda4f25cff22148a218d3acfc6eb6929806","tid":1308151,"uid":113626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋自己煮野菜煎雞一定好健康 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d68ed5b051aefe6d38a44232a9ce6e36124b8af","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:50:13.000Z","msg":"鰹魚湯英國呢面唐人街有得賣，香港應該大撚把地方有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994017db31377f9fb92db94492c07cd2f1fab332","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497ea987ec7e74a6839e9f4420d4897d29f6c80c","tid":1308151,"uid":157735,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:32:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">求埋野菜煎雞飯<br />\n樓主一生平安</span>"},{"pid":"c7ff561a31fcf389201bbe1946d240ffd45b653c","tid":1308151,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"693b7edb87c4cbfc64235774e2f66a5de9e8705f","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"497ea987ec7e74a6839e9f4420d4897d29f6c80c","tid":1308151,"uid":157735,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:32:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">求埋野菜煎雞飯<br />\n樓主一生平安</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:54:07.000Z","msg":"其實都係果D料，係個汁唔要薑同蒜頭，雞扒洗完，印乾醃左佢，都係鹽同黑椒薑粉蒜頭粉之類（呢面係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n煎香兩邊雞扒，倒返果堆味琳，豉油，酒同糖，煮撚到佢稠，搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n菜......我估佢都係落鹽白烚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮乜都係，最緊要試味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煎塊牛扒仲煩過呢兩個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c853478f3a4bdd239268ff75febc223767d69cbc","tid":1308151,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d68ed5b051aefe6d38a44232a9ce6e36124b8af","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:50:13.000Z","msg":"鰹魚湯英國呢面唐人街有得賣，香港應該大撚把地方有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:55:16.000Z","msg":"吉之島一定有<br />\n平時老母買嚟煮嘢煲湯成日用"},{"pid":"e1ea8eb35bfa9cef46b3df5db5689622319b28f6","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c853478f3a4bdd239268ff75febc223767d69cbc","tid":1308151,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d68ed5b051aefe6d38a44232a9ce6e36124b8af","tid":1308151,"uid":22054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:50:13.000Z","msg":"鰹魚湯英國呢面唐人街有得賣，香港應該大撚把地方有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:55:16.000Z","msg":"吉之島一定有<br />\n平時老母買嚟煮嘢煲湯成日用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:59:53.000Z","msg":"買粉開就得，唔洗用靚野，足料湯包果D呢面10鎊一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開粉果D 2鎊幾定3鎊一盒仔，入面8包粉，一包用幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c